* Requirements
 
 * mono >= 2.0
 * mono-posix >= 2.0
 * mono-cairo >= 2.0
 * gstreamer >= 0.10.22
 * gnonlin >= 0.10.10
 * gtk-sharp >= 2.12
 * db40 >= 6.0


* Download
  LongoMatch source tarballs are available on gnome FTP:
   http://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/sources/longomatch/0.15/

  See the website for distribution-specific packages.

